      "id": "if-else-if-intro",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 3. The `if-else-if` Ladder\n\nWhen you have multiple conditions to check.\n\n### Syntax:\n```java\nif (condition1) {\n    // code if condition1 is true\n} else if (condition2) {\n    // code if condition2 is true\n} else if (condition3) {\n    // code if condition3 is true\n} else {\n    // code if all conditions are false\n}\n```\n\nJava checks conditions from top to bottom and executes the first block where the condition is true.",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "id": "if-else-if-intro"
      }
    },
