      "id": "when-to-use",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## When to Use What?\n\n| Situation | Use |\n|-----------|-----|\n| Simple yes/no decision | `if-else` |\n| Multiple ranges to check | `if-else-if` |\n| Many specific values | `switch` |\n| Multiple conditions that ALL must be true | `if` with `&&` |\n| Multiple conditions where ANY can be true | `if` with `\\|\\|` |\n| Quick inline decision | Ternary operator |",
